* TEXT-T02 = Select a View
*
* TEXT-E01 = Invalid Material
* TEXT-E02 = Enter a change date
* TEXT-E03 = Date specified is in the future, enter a valid date
* TEXT-E04 = Invalid Material Type
* TEXT-E05 = No data found.
*
* TEXT-H01 = Material Master Report
* TEXT-H02 = Material Audit View
*
* TEXT-C01 = Material
* TEXT-C02 = Changed On
* TEXT-C03 = Change Time
* TEXT-C04 = Changed By
* TEXT-C05 = Table
* TEXT-C06 = Field
* TEXT-C07 = Change Type
* TEXT-C08 = Old Contents
* TEXT-C09 = New Contents
* TEXT-C10 = Table Key
* TEXT-C11 = Change Object
* TEXT-C12 = Object Value
